data.meta_description: Gundakar Liechtenstein was born on January 30, 1580 in Eisgrub, son of Hartmann 4 Von Liechtenstein-Nikolsburg-Feldsberg and Anna Maria Von Ortenburg. He was married  to Agnes Van Ostfriesland, they had 2 children. He was married  to Elzbieta Lukrecja Princess Of Teschen. He died on July  5, 1658. This information is part of Family tree Baris by Paul Baris on Genealogy Online.
